'''Infinity Plus Two'''（前称'''Infinite Interactive'''），是一个游戏开发商，总部设在[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]][[維多利亞州|维多利亚]][[墨尔本|墨尔本]]。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.infinite-interactive.com/company.php | title = Infinite Interactive - Company | accessdate = 2013-10-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110810111232/http://www.infinite-interactive.com/company.php | archive-date = 2011-08-10 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>该公司由史蒂夫·福克纳在1989年成立，与SSG合作开发Warlords系列游戏，史蒂夫在2003年将公司完全独立。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamerbytes.com/2009/03/gamerbytes_interview_travellin.php | title = PSN, XBLA: GamerBytes Interview: Traveling The Galactrix With Steve Fawkner | date = 2009-03-16 | accessdate = 2009-05-20 | archive-date = 2011-08-24 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/61AzAeqZR?url=http://www.gamasutra.com/topic/console-digital/gamerbytes/2009/03/gamerbytes_interview_travellin.php | dead-url = no }}</ref>2011年，该公司被[[火猴工作室|Firemint]]收购。然而，在2012年末该公司宣布他们重新成为一家独立的开发公司<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.infinite-interactive.com/were-back/ |title=We're Back |date=14 September 2012 |accessdate=5 January 2013 |publisher=Infinite Interactive |first=Andrew |last=Castenmiller |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151107181250/http://www.infinite-interactive.com/were-back/ |archive-date=2015-11-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2019年，公司从Infinite Interactive更名为“Infinity Plus Two”。2021年1月，公司宣布作价450万美元被[[505游戏|505游戏]]收购，成为505游戏旗下第三家游戏开发工作室。<ref>[https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2021-01-14-505-games-acquires-infinity-plus-two 505 Games acquires Infinity Plus Two] {{Wayback|url=https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2021-01-14-505-games-acquires-infinity-plus-two |date=20210603112436 }}.GameIndustry.2021-01-14.[2021-02-11].</ref>

